# No Browser Verification

Do not open, navigate, or verify changes in a browser unless the user explicitly asks for it.

- Do not use browser automation, MCP browser tools, or screenshots to confirm UI work.
- Rely on code review, static analysis, lints, and tests instead.
- If visual confirmation would help, describe what to check rather than opening a browser yourself.
